descriptions: You can download a trial version of this app to try it for 15 minutes for free.
You won’t be charged anything when this free trial ends. You can’t make in-app purchases or use add-on content during this free trial, but you’ll keep any achievements you earn.

display_long_description:
🎮 Endless Overtake is an adrenaline-fueled VR racing experience where skillful driving meets high-speed chaos. Your mission: overtake traffic, drive dangerously, and reach the highest score possible — all without crashing!

|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|

# 🧠 Core Gameplay

- 🚗 Overtake cars closely

- ⚡Drive at high speeds

- 🔁 Go against traffic

- 💥 Avoid crashes to keep your run alive


[media]

|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|

# 🛠️ Customization & Upgrades

- 🎨 Change your car’s color

- 🪶 Add spoilers and new wheels

- 💰 Upgrade your vehicle’s performance


[media]

|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|

# 🎯 Game Modes

- 🛣️ One-Way Traffic – Classic endless mode

- ↔️ Two-Way Traffic – Double lanes, double challenge

- 💣 Bomb Alert – Keep your speed up or explode!

- ⏱️ Time Attack – Beat the clock to survive


[media]

|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------| 

# 🌆 Maps & Environments

- 🛤️ Highway – Long roads with high speeds

- 🏙️ City – Tight streets and tough traffic

- 🌉 Bridge – Narrow and intense driving experience

[media]
